# homeoremedica API Examples
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = your-firebase-id-token-here

### Get user session
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/session
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get usage stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/usage
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Find remedies
POST {{baseUrl}}/find
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "all",
  "symptoms": ["fever", "anxiety", "headache"]
}

### Find remedies - specific book
POST {{baseUrl}}/find
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "boericke-MM",
  "symptoms": ["thirst", "restlessness"]
}

### Get all cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a new case
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Patient with fever and anxiety",
  "note": "Acute onset, very restless",
  "bookId": "boericke-MM",
  "symptoms": ["fever", "anxiety", "restlessness"],
  "results": [
    {
      "remedyId": "acon-b",
      "score": 30
    }
  ]
}

### Update a case
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cases/case-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated case title",
  "note": "Additional notes after follow-up"
}

### Delete a case
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cases/case-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
